title: Morning Joe 3/16/21
description: Two people were arrested and charged in connection with assaulting U.S. Capitol Police Officer Brian Sicknick, but federal authorities stopped short of charging them with his death, according to court documents. The Morning Joe panel discusses.
author: news.podcasts@nbcuni.com (NBC News)
